{"tid":1393091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選舉事務處：2019年約有411萬9千名選民 較去年淨增加約30萬5千名選民","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T03:44:30.000Z","uid":31542,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6de2a0869b62ae91a13865dcd78593e4b45bc570","tid":1393091,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:28:20.000Z","msg":"2019年地方選區臨時選民登記冊有約411萬9千名選民，較去年淨增加約30萬5千名，當中已計算約38萬6千名新登記選民及扣減了約3萬2千名因離世和4萬9千名經查訊程序等原因而被載入取消登記名單內的選民。<br />\n<br />\n一手資料 朋友係入面做 岩岩開會講<br />\n新聞公報都未有<br />\n如果截止日期前交左表嘅話<br />\n可以上選舉事務處個網查閱下<br />\n確認信會遲下寄出"},{"pid":"c2ffc809c56a1ccb4417976a68f03200933c28dc","tid":1393091,"uid":78695,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/p6SPF3E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fp6SPF3E.gif&h=6818fdd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7a10827be13bb42d825ac0b7fc00d3c56241b0c","tid":1393091,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"睇到無乜感覺<br />\n制度內同佢玩無意思"},{"pid":"302ec0f62efa8169e24e5de9431f8bfe5c022536","tid":1393091,"uid":260923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:29:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb7680351e692843960bc2ae9e1a1a22deb486a0","tid":1393091,"uid":162316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"最後數字都係得30萬?"},{"pid":"5df7a4496896623e90a6e0fc4b45934b0ceb32ac","tid":1393091,"uid":31542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c7a10827be13bb42d825ac0b7fc00d3c56241b0c","tid":1393091,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"睇到無乜感覺<br />\n制度內同佢玩無意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:33:19.000Z","msg":"一步一步黎 起碼都有400萬人做選民"},{"pid":"6c832a35469256e8377f1f12ba817f2618b80a5b","tid":1393091,"uid":30478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08